high_descs: Go straight, then turn left into the hallway and all the way into the last room, then left to the small circular coffeetable.
Pick up the mango from the table.
Leave the room the way you came in, go straight and then right into the kitchen area to the microwave.
Use the microwave on the mango.
Turn around back to the hallway, turn right and go straight into the room ahead, then turn right to the small diningtable with two chairs in front of it.
Place the mango on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved mango on a diningtable.

high_descs: Head out the kitchen and turn left to walk to the end of the passage and hang left to reach the round coffeetable.
Pick up the yellow mango from the round table.
Turn right and enter the passage on the right to walk to the kitchen on the right to reach the microwave.
Heat the yellow mango in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and walk to the passage and turn right to the end of the passage and turn right at the shelf to reach the diningtable.
Put the mango on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mango on the diningtable.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the coffee table
Take the fruit from the coffee table
Turn around and go near the microwave
Put the fruit into the microwave
Take it out and go near the dining table
Put the fruit on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Placed the fruit on the dining table
